OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,FNottinghamshire Live, the local
OL,7,Fnewspaper service in Nottingham, have
OL,8,Fbeen told Reform UK's Nottinghamshire
OL,9,Fcounty councillors will not speak to
OL,10,Fany of its journalists.
OL,12,FThe ban means that local paper
OL,13,Freporters and Local Democracy
OL,14,Freporters, of which ITV News Central
OL,15,Fand other news outlets often use,
OL,16,Fcannot talk to councillors in any
OL,17,Fcapacity, except in emergency
OL,18,Fscenarios.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
