OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,FIt covers the entire team of 41
OL,7,Fcouncillors, meaning that the paper,
OL,8,Fwhich has been delivering news to the
OL,9,Fcity since 1878, can only talk to
OL,10,Fcouncillors in scenarios like flooding
OL,11,For incidents at council-run schools.
OL,13,FReporters and unions are now concerned
OL,14,Fabout the ramifications of shutting
OL,15,Fout journalists.
OL,17,FThe reason why the ban came into place
OL,18,Fwas because of an article written by
OL,19,Fjournalist Oliver Pridmore.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
