OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1756487219
OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,FIt was claimed in the piece that two
OL,7,FReform county councillors would be
OL,8,Fsuspended from their county council
OL,9,Fgroup if they did not vote for Council
OL,10,FLeader Mick Barton's preference of a
OL,11,Fbigger Nottingham covering Broxtowe
OL,12,Fand Gedling.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Central he said he was
OL,15,Fbewildered by the ban.
OL,17,FHe said: "Speechless when I first
OL,18,Fheard. We're not on any war against
OL,19,FReform at NottinghamshireLive in the
OL,20,Fslightest.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
