OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,FChris Morley from the National Union
OL,7,Fof Journalists said: "If it seems to
OL,8,Fbe acceptable that those in power can
OL,9,Fdo this sort of thing, then other
OL,10,Fpeople might get a taste for it.
OL,12,F"I think the party concerned can
OL,13,Fexpect a really big backlash from the
OL,14,Fpublic".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
