OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1756487219
OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,F"They should communicate - people want
OL,7,Fto know what's going on."
OL,9,F"The whole point is, Reform want to be
OL,10,Fthe people's party, yet they've
OL,11,Fstopped talking to media outlets. It's
OL,12,Fjust not right."
OL,14,FIn response, Nottinghamshire County
OL,15,FCouncil said: "The Reform Group at
OL,16,FNottinghamshire County Council has
OL,17,Fbanned proactive engagement with
OL,18,Fjournalists from Nottinghamshire Live
OL,19,Fand the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,20,FService (LDRS).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
