OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1756487219
OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,F"The ban, which will only be lifted
OL,7,Ffor emergency scenarios like flooding
OL,8,Fand weather-related cases, incidents
OL,9,Fat council-run schools, adult social
OL,10,Fcare, or public safety issues, has
OL,11,Fcome into immediate effect...
OL,13,FReporters from Nottinghamshire Live
OL,14,Fand LDRS will continue to attend
OL,15,Fpublic meetings."
OL,17,FITV News Central also received no
OL,18,Fcomment from the national Reform Party
OL,19,For Lee Anderson, the Reform MP for
OL,20,FAshfield.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
