OL,3,CReform councillors' media blackout
OL,4,Ccondemned as blow to democracy
OL,6,FClaire Ward, East Midlands Mayor
OL,7,F(Labour) said: "A free press is one of
OL,8,Fthe cornerstones of our democracy.
OL,10,F"I'm disappointed that Reform have
OL,11,Fadopted this stance.
OL,13,F"It doesn't help anyone to understand
OL,14,Fthe challenges faced when running
OL,15,Flocal councils or making big decisions.
OL,17,F"I will continue to engage with all
OL,18,Flocal press, and hope that Reform will
OL,19,Freconsider".
